        "conbody": {
            "section": {
                "p": [
                    "When you share an item, such as a document, a folder, or an alert, you send a notification to the people you have shared the item with.  When someone shares an item with you, you will receive a notification about it.  Notifications are also sent when you or someone else stops sharing an item that has been shared, or adds or removes an item in a shared folder.",
                    {
                        "uicontrol": [
                            {
                                "#tail": "from the",
                                "#text": "Notifications"
                            },
                            {
                                "#tail": "drop-down list at the top of any page, or you can view the",
                                "#text": "More"
                            },
                            {
                                "#tail": "pod on the",
                                "#text": "Notifications"
                            }
                        ],
                        "ph": {
                            "@keyref": "prodnamefirst",
                            "#tail": "home page."
                        },
                        "#text": "To see the list of all the notifications you have sent or received, you can either select"
                    },
                    {
                        "uicontrol": {
                            "#tail": "page.",
                            "#text": "Settings > General"
                        },
                        "#text": "If you prefer not to receive notifications, you can turn them off for one or all of the event types on the"
                    }
                ]
            }
        }
    }
